{"tid":2288001,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"罐頭鮑魚 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-11-16T07:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T08:43:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"765a35ff6916ecafc7cb2bd7deb7c6333cf20900","tid":2288001,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T07:34:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201116/XEPJ4QGRLZFCLOHBQBMPMGI3KQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201116%2FXEPJ4QGRLZFCLOHBQBMPMGI3KQ%2F&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu63e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=19ba423f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201116%2FXEPJ4QGRLZFCLOHBQBMPMGI3KQ%2F&h=1a4e5f37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201116/XEPJ4QGRLZFCLOHBQBMPMGI3KQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n罐頭鮑魚 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EfkSAgkXPT9cC5_03_WhaSBeFt8=/960x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JZHAESWUCNA7DCJFTCWLVZHJPI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEfkSAgkXPT9cC5_03_WhaSBeFt8%3D%2F960x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJZHAESWUCNA7DCJFTCWLVZHJPI.jpg&h=32a3e6da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科一名督察，涉嫌在警署偷竊頭盔、手套、罐頭鮑魚、相機電池等物品被捕，令輿論震驚。<br />\n<br />\n魚蛋革命之後，香港警察形象轉為負面。去年反送中以來，警察形象只能以不堪來形容，尤其是721之後，香港警察完全失去巿民信任，兵賊是否一家，是許多香港人心中的疑團。這個疑團，歷史終將給出答案，大家拭目以待。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n。香港人早已習慣在港聞版讀到警察醜聞。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n邏輯上比較合理的推斷是，很多警察已經習慣於犯法，從執勤時進入便利店隨手拿取一樽水，被踢爆後「後數」，到涉嫌偷睇裙底、非禮、強姦、高買、販毒等等，無惡不作。這批特權份子，似乎認為自己有凌駕法律的權利，一般巿民需要遵守法律，他們認為自己不需要。一般人敬畏法制，害怕受到法律制裁，犯法代價太大，不敢輕易挑釁法律，犯法前必會三思。為幾隻罐頭鮑魚、幾排相機電池犯罪，「得到」的，與很可能要付出的代價絕不成正比，沒有甚麼人會鋌而走險。香港警察甘願冒險，不是不懂得計數，也不是愚勇，而是早已經麻木。<br />\n<br />\n逢星期一至六刊登"},{"pid":"72818d1141e004da9630f60d573be2fb3703a84d","tid":2288001,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T08:43:30.000Z","msg":"所以要封鎖壹周刊記者偽造訪問嘅真相<br />\n以免香港人知道"}]}